{"tid":228271,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"美心臨時工(母親節)","createTime":"2017-05-03T18:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T02:43:31.000Z","uid":68182,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0100b1c3a4d9602b981e75cb2b189525364652f","tid":228271,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:16:40.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打做過佢果d倉務員 生產助理員 餅處理員<br />\n見都有五十幾蚊幾好pay<br />\n環境點樣 工作性質<br />\n有冇得傾下計 伏唔伏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4cce66027d1278f900107f1020670a089e7085","tid":228271,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:17:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8bed8cd6d9d7b252caa83fb802ebbb982743c36","tid":228271,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:18:06.000Z","msg":"加班加到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜更先好少少"},{"pid":"b3bf52ed5d91e58b7397faa4248623d20adb0ab2","tid":228271,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:18:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有 悶到傻 成個機械人咁</blockquote><br />\n巴打返咩位？<br />\n一返工做同樣既野做到收工？<br />\n有冇得抖下"},{"pid":"61a04697b3d72d2d48e8590036e2d2a473bdde51","tid":228271,"uid":30061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:18:51.000Z","msg":"聽講好閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b334065db132b62891ead2e3d3ee4dc3daa2aa","tid":228271,"uid":68182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:19:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加班加到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜更先好少少</blockquote><br />\n咩位都要加班？<br />\n本身缺錢 <br />\n有得抖下加班冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1986ac3107f73af564fed6354e14cf3456dc861","tid":228271,"u