{"pid":"cda4086a9638501b34d5097f9b764c555c905403","tid":228271,"uid":48895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:36:24.000Z","msg":"又準備睇一車車後生仔入垃圾美心工廠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真心搵過第二份喇...美心月餅工廠唔係人做架<br />\n西餅都唔好得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06dad7514349b0a7017f2b0c0d8083996c251f16","tid":228271,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:05:56.000Z","msg":"ed垃圾閪工昆鳩d無學歷/學生哥學生妹入去做既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8c46c82d3785746d3e90c5a2b9ff4dcee916d3","tid":228271,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:46:14.000Z","msg":"西餅廠最撚西。<br />\n<br />\n月餅廠玩過，好彩入hea位，日日同女吹水吹一日"},{"pid":"ebb40882fdf54ce9a89d6817bc2022ebf5a9dfaf","tid":228271,"uid":33721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西餅廠最撚西。<br />\n<br />\n月餅廠玩過，好彩入hea位，日日同女吹水吹一日</blockquote><br />\n西餅二樓先正 夜班全部位都輕鬆到爆"},{"pid":"bf401abd1f4f22bc46667401120c000c6f8919b1","tid":228271,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:59:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>西餅廠最撚西。<br />\n<br />\n月餅廠玩過，好彩入hea位，日日同女吹水吹一日</blockquote><br />\n西餅二樓先正 夜班全部位都輕鬆到爆</blockquote><br />\n夜班嘛⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n我記得係月餅廠有日比人強逼去包裝郭，我屌佢老母，要人手疊月餅箱，仲要大箱五層，含家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，仲要派個老野幫我，真撚係多撚謝你，我一條友抬都好撚過佢。<br />\n<br />\n仲問我叫咩名，擺到明想調我落去，我鳩吹個假名比佢。到收工果時仲叫我ot，都on撚柒鳩，應承佢之後更係去飯堂hea到六點半直接收工坐車走，之後兩日射波，再番hea位同班dse妹妹吹水。"},{"pid":"cecf80971a25b0ded85434340e80be34853faed5","tid":228271,"uid":47184,"like":0,"dislike":0,